Last Updated July 2025

You can use Oracle REST APIs to view and manage data stored in Oracle Supply Chain Management Cloud.

Whether you're experienced with or new to REST, use this guide to find what you need, including:

  • A quick start that walks you through a simple request example.
  • Detailed descriptions for each REST API resource.

request.name: Delete rate details for selected resource rates

description.content: Delete rate details for selected resource rates edited using the Perform Mass Edit capability in the Resource Rates page.

(Required) This is the hash key of the attributes which make up the composite key for the Resource Rates resource and used to uniquely identify an instance of Resource Rates.
